who threw a fox trap over his head...

57
00:06:31,880 --> 00:06:34,440
A gun! Is it real?

58
00:06:34,520 --> 00:06:37,119
It's a water pistol.
But you can't shoot it inside.

59
00:06:37,200 --> 00:06:40,479
But at the country house this summer,
we can shoot.

60
00:06:44,439 --> 00:06:48,240
-Did you miss your dad?
-Not much.

61
00:06:48,320 --> 00:06:52,280
